<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٦٢٨ - <span class="c2">«إذا شربتم اللبن فتمضمضوا منه فإن له دسما»</span> .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
